snippet.title: Block Strategy - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Block Strategy is an RTS game where the world is made up of blocks that can be placed or destroyed to change the terrain.

Release date is currently the second half of 2024.

Please wishlist on steam at the following link: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2642070/Block_Strategy/

Music by James Elsey
